change_start: change_start: Change the bot start character spaces also count(this will be case sensitive)
hello: hello: Reply hello with the user"s name
echo: echo: Repeat what is said after
logs: logs: Set the logs channel to be sent the logs
lock: lock: Toggling locking the bot to be only used in the default channel or server-wide
long_reference: long_reference: Enable long reference, reply any message with the word "long" with long reference image
encrypt: encrypt: Encrypt your message with a special encryption type(be fast, the message will be deleted after 5 seconds)
decrypt: decrypt: Decrypt your message with a special encryption type(be fast, the message will be deleted after 5 seconds)
